title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Sep 29 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Sep 29 2021
description:
Tennessee Senator Marsha Blackburn joins C&B, predicts what Dems will do this week on infrastructure, budget, debt ceiling, border, Afghanistan. Democrats want to spend billions on tree equity. LeBron James speaks on vaccines. Texas Governor Greg Abbott updates us on the situation at the border. Colbert dances with vaccines.
